					</div>
				</span>
				<div class="clear"></div>
				<div class="body">
					<p>Hendrik: We are actually using node-gently which I've written: <a rel="nofollow" href="http://github.com/felixge/node-gently">http://github.com/felixge/node-gently</a></p>
<p>I would not recommend it at this point, as I'm in the process of coming up with a more comprehensive module. That being said, I have used it for pretty much everything we do with transloadit, so it's certainly working. However, it only covers the very basics of stubbing a method and returning fake results for test purposes.</p>
